*** Code Style
$ â€” global vars
obj can refs only to global and child obj
use explicit return
right:
	foo = ->
		...
		return result
wrong:
	foo = ->
		...
		result

use @ for treatment to the instance variables and methods
right:
	@foo
wrong
	this.foo

in other ways use this
right:
	return this
wrong:
	return @